This paper deals with image restoration, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also introduces a new regularizer, which is a mathematical concept that is often used in machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Finally, the paper uses experimental results to demonstrate the effectiveness of the proposed method, which is a common approach in data science (cs.DS).
